# Neon Postgres connection string.
# Neon dashboard -> your project -> Connection string -> "Prisma" / "Pooled connection".
# Keep the ?sslmode=require part. For Vercel runtime use the POOLED connection and
# add &pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1 to play nice with serverless.
#
# Example:
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@ep-xxxx-pooler.eu-central-1.aws.neon.tech/kg?sslmode=require&pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1"
